data_table.description: Osteoporosis Study - Whole Body DXA, Original Cohort Exams 22 - 24. This dataset includes body composition data from Framingham Original Cohort measured using dual x-ray absorptiometry (DXA), including fat mass, soft tissue, and bone mineral content (BMC) and density (BMD) variables. The whole body scan was performed at Exam 22 and then again at Exam 23.
